name: Vintage Tin Doll, "Ginger"
description:
Assemblage Art

Vintage spice tin makes the body of this Hollywood Star inspired piece.  
Striking face and legs made of porcelain doll pieces.  
Arms of bead and wire.    
Crystal wand, jewelry piece headband, and feather boa add a touch of glamor. 

Wonderful piece for anywhere in the home.  Great, Unique gift!

name: Vintage Tin Doll, "Skidoo"
description:
Assemblage Art

Vintage Skidoo Tin, wire, porcelain, jewelry, bottle caps,  metal reflectors, beads, and other materials make this wonderful piece. 

Hang her up in any room of the house, or give as a great, unique gift.  

About a foot long.

name: Paper Mache and Tin Ghost
description:
Darling Halloween Piece!

Paper mache Boo! face sits on vintage tin.  Beaded orange and black arms.  Holding a key in one hand and lock in the other.  Chain legs dangle when placed on edge of table or shelf. 

Other materials include wire and bottle cap. 

Spook-tacular addition to your Halloween decor collection!

name: Vintage Tin Witch
description:
You'll cackle with delight at our delightful Halloween inspired piece. 

Paper mache face and green vintage spice tin make this wonderful piece.   Beaded legs and wire arms.   Crystals to give her a Halloween glow 

Clock in hand lets you know, its bewitching hour! 

Metal hook on back to hang her in any room during the Halloween season.

name: Vintage Tin Doll, "English Rose"
description:
A personal favorite...

English tea inspired.  

Round black vintage tin with pink flower bunch and gold dots.  Charming porcelain face, hands, and legs.   
Salt shaker hat and beaded legs. 

Metal hook on back to hang. 

This lovely lady will be a wonderful addition to any room.
